<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Your OTP Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #0f172a;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #1e293b;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #0ea5e9;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
    }

    .otp-box {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }

    .otp-digit {
      background-color: #334155;
      color: #38bdf8;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: #0f172a;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .content, .header, .footer {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .otp-box {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .otp-digit {
        padding: 12px 16px;
        font-size: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Verify Your Email üîê</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{data.firstName}},</p>
      <p>Use the following one-time password (OTP) to verify your email address. This code will expire in 5 minutes.</p>

      <div class="otp-box">
        {{#each data.otp}}
          <div class="otp-digit">{{this}}</div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>

      <p>If you didn‚Äôt request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      Stay secure,<br />
      ‚Äî The ArchKalinga Team
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
